OL,3,CPremier League sees off Man City-led
OL,4,CAPT rules challenge but divisions
OL,5,Cremain
OL,7,FThe Premier League has headed off a
OL,8,Fpotentially very damaging challenge,
OL,9,Fled by Manchester City, as clubs voted
OL,10,Fto approve its amendments to the
OL,11,FLeague's rules on Associated Party
OL,12,FTransactions (APTs).
OL,14,FHad it lost it would very much have
OL,15,Flooked like it was the reigning
OL,16,Fchampions steering the ship not the
OL,17,FLeague itself.
OL,19,FNevertheless, the fact that the vote
OL,20,Fwas not unanimous has highlighted
OL,21,Fdivisions within the league.
