OL,7,FThe showdown was over the extent to
OL,8,Fwhich APTs limit the amount of cash
OL,9,Fcompanies closely associated with
OL,10,Fclubs can hand over. The rules are in
OL,11,Fplace to prevent owners with almost
OL,12,Flimitless resources from pumping so
OL,13,Fmuch cash into their clubs, that
OL,14,Fothers struggle to compete.
OL,16,FCity triggered a tribunal over the
OL,17,FLeague's APTs limitations and
OL,18,Fexperienced partial success when the
OL,19,Fpanel decided some of the rules were
OL,20,Funlawful.
