OL,7,FThey had initiated the arbitration in
OL,8,Fthe first place after the Premier
OL,9,FLeague rejected a sponsorship deal
OL,10,Fthey'd made for not being of fair
OL,11,Fmarket value. In other words they
OL,12,Fdeemed it an artificially inflated
OL,13,Ffigure.
OL,15,FThe Premier League wanted a quick
OL,16,Fresolution to the tribunal's findings
OL,17,Fand had tabled amendments to the APT
OL,18,Frules.
