OL,7,FCity had support from Aston Villa in
OL,8,Fwanting to delay today's vote until
OL,9,Fthe full tribunal interpretation was
OL,10,Fpublished, but they failed to get the
OL,11,Ffurther five votes required to have
OL,12,Fwon the day.
OL,14,FIn a statement the League said: "The
OL,15,FPremier League has conducted a
OL,16,Fdetailed consultation with clubs -
OL,17,Finformed by multiple opinions from
OL,18,Fexpert, independent Leading Counsel -
OL,19,Fto draft rule changes that address
OL,20,Famendments required to the system.
