OL,7,F"This relates to integrating the
OL,8,Fassessment of Shareholder loans, the
OL,9,Fremoval of some of the amendments made
OL,10,Fto APT rules earlier this year and
OL,11,Fchanges to the process by which
OL,12,Frelevant information from the League's
OL,13,F'databank' is shared with a club's
OL,14,Fadvisors."
