OL,7,FIt went on: "The purpose of the APT
OL,8,Frules is to ensure clubs are not able
OL,9,Fto benefit from commercial deals or
OL,10,Freductions in costs that are not at
OL,11,FFair Market Value (FMV) by virtue of
OL,12,Frelationships with Associated Parties.
OL,13,FThese rules were introduced to provide
OL,14,Fa robust mechanism to safeguard the
OL,15,Ffinancial stability, integrity and
OL,16,Fcompetitive balance of the League."
